*'''Hyphenation:''' ma·rine
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-iːn|-iːn]]

===Adjective===
'''marine''' 
# Of or, or pertaining to, the sea (marine ''biology'', marine ''insurance'')
# (''Capitalized'') Of or, or pertaining to, a [[marine corps]].

===Noun===
'''marine''' (''plural:'' [[marines]])
# A member of a [[marine corps]]

